WEBVTT

00:09:59.187 --> 00:10:02.000
preventing us from getting
from here to there.

00:10:02.024 --> 00:10:04.439
But the good news is, we exist,

00:10:04.463 --> 00:10:07.898
and there is a vast amount
of untapped potential over here.

00:10:08.802 --> 00:10:12.498
Good news number two,
and this is really good news:

00:10:13.411 --> 00:10:17.345
films by and about women make more money.

00:10:17.369 --> 00:10:20.493
Yes! Yes! It's true!

00:10:20.517 --> 00:10:21.853
(Cheers and applause)

00:10:21.877 --> 00:10:23.521
It's true.

00:10:23.545 --> 00:10:25.864
The Washington Post
recently released a study

00:10:25.888 --> 00:10:30.696
showing that films that feature women
make 23 cents more on every dollar